title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table within a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() function.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the expected result is that the data should be exported without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 1. Insert one table into a grid cell. 2. Insert another table into another grid cell.
